Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:26.10,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,STAND UP まだ僕を呼んでる声が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:31.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,「YES」だって「NO」だって 関係はないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:36.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,STARDUST 穴だらけのゲームスコア
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:41.74,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,DEAD OR LIE DEAD OR LIE　自由を見たくて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:46.45,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,GO OUT 閉ざされた夜に I'll be eaten away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:51.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,透明な武器を手に入れてる LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:56.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんの為に　何を守る　長い待ちは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:01.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ぶち壞すこの彈丸で！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:06.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER LIE モノクロな光のない世界でも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:11.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER END NEVER LIE　心は染まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:17.52,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,THE END OF WORLD　絕望に僅かな希望握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:26.45,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,震える指で狙い定めて 未來を探せ！
Comment: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:21.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————OPCN——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:26.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,STAND UP 呼唤我的声音未绝于耳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:31.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,无论答案是「YES」或「NO」 都没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:36.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,STARDUST 游戏结果已满是漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:41.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,DEAD OR LIE DEAD OR LIE 希冀能看到自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:46.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,GO OUT 在这憋闷的夜晚 我终将被腐蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:51.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,无形的武器已然到手 LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:56.96,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了什么 要守护什么 才经过漫长等待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:01.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就用这颗子弹破坏一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:06.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER LIE 即使在这仅剩黑白 暗无光辉的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:11.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER END NEVER LIE 心灵绝不沾染黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:17.52,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,THE END OF WORLD 在绝望中握住仅存的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:26.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,用颤抖的手指瞄准目标 去追寻未来！
Comment: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:47.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDJP——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:58.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終わりが始まるアリアと共に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:03.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白旗を掲げた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:09.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脱獄の果てに歓声の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:13.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手錠突き付けられ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:19.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ほら、見て　愚かな駒よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:24.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}断罪の茶番
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:26.93,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}独壇場Funky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.93,0:22:29.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その目で見ろ　競争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:34.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}Forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:34.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:37.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多発的な展開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:40.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人の波を掻き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.78,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫べ　My Justice，Right Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:45.16,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Make it a vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:47.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感心できるのはFunky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:50.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喪失だけが拒止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:55.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}導いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:58.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鮮烈過ぎた年回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:23:00.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏見のあるカテゴライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.34,0:23:02.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't believe no story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:04.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I know you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.60,0:23:06.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No, we're already over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.47,0:23:08.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Everybody loves despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:11.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I'll sadly go from the end
Comment: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:48.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDCN——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:58.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伴随着结尾即开始的咏叹调
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:03.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高举白旗的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:09.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃狱后的欢呼声中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:13.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被强行拷上了手铐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:19.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:24.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这定罪的把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:26.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇异的独角戏舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.93,0:22:29.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看着 竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:34.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遗落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:34.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺骗吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:37.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多线并行的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:40.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拨开人群
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊着 这是我正义的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:45.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}许下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:47.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得赞美的惊恐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:50.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯独拒绝丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:55.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:58.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}过于艳丽的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:23:00.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}带有偏见的分类
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.34,0:23:02.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:04.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.60,0:23:06.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我们已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.47,0:23:08.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人人都爱着绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:11.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会满怀悲伤地离去
